OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FItalians wait for rain     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwhere longest river runs   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdry                        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, On a farm in northern Italy not far    
OL,6, from the Adriatic Sea, Giampaolo       
OL,7, Bassi's crops are in trouble.          
OL,9,F"Salty water is killing the plants     
OL,10,Fbecause they can't stand such a high   
OL,11,Fconcentration," the 32-year-old says.  
OL,13,FHe pulls up one of the more sickly     
OL,14,Flooking plants and, where you should   
OL,15,Fsee peanuts dangling from the root,    
OL,16,Fthere's nothing.                       
OL,18,FGiampaolo has had problems with salt in
OL,19,Fthe water before, but not like this.   
